In the Matter of Iris R. Lewis. Jewish Child Care Association of New York, Appellant, Mollie Lewis et al., Respondents.

Order, entered on June 20, 1962, unanimously affirmed, without costs. The order of this court entered on June 20, 1963 is vacated. No opinion. Concur — ■ Breitel, J. P., Rabin, McNally, Eager and Steuer, JJ.
